Malawi Gay Marriage We hear from the brother-in-law of one half of the Malawian couple facing imprisonment for being gay. Life in the Rift Valley Two years after the violent aftermath of Kenya's general election, Michael Kaloki revisits one of the worst affected areas. The 'Whale Man' British photographer Duncan Murrell tells Ritula Shah how he used a kayak to get close enough to capture stunning photographs of humpback whales. Show less